<body>
<div class="wrap">
<h1>Test Survey Email Create</h1>
<p class="lead">Tests email creation against the SFMC Content Builder REST API. Maps SOAP <code>Create Email</code> fields (Name, Subject, HTMLBody, CategoryID, IsHTMLPaste) to REST asset payloads.</p>
%%[IF @showForm == "true" THEN]%%
<div class="card">
<form method="get" action="%%=RequestParameter('PAGEURL')=%%">
<input type="hidden" name="create" value="1">
<label for="itemBaseName">Email name</label>
<input type="text" id="itemBaseName" name="itemBaseName" placeholder="Survey_Test_%%=Format(Now(),'yyyyMMdd_HHmmss')=%%" required>
<label for="emailSubjectLine">Subject</label>
<input type="text" id="emailSubjectLine" name="emailSubjectLine" value="Survey" required>
<label for="sourceEmailId">Source asset ID</label>
<input type="text" id="sourceEmailId" name="sourceEmailId" inputmode="numeric" pattern="[0-9]+" placeholder="e.g. 56191 (type 4 template) or survey email asset ID" required>
<label for="categoryId">Category ID (folder)</label>
<input type="text" id="categoryId" name="categoryId" inputmode="numeric" pattern="[0-9]+" placeholder="e.g. 58374">
<label for="mode">Create mode</label>
<select id="mode" name="mode">
<option value="rest207from4" selected>rest207from4 — create from parent template only (type 4 → 207)</option>
<option value="rest207">rest207 — clone survey-template email (type 207)</option>
<option value="rest208">rest208 — HTML paste (SOAP IsHTMLPaste equivalent)</option>
</select>
<div class="actions">
<button type="submit" class="btn-primary">Create test email</button>
</div>
</form>
</div>
<div class="map">
<p><strong>SOAP → REST mapping</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><code>Name</code> → <code>name</code></li>
<li><code>Subject</code> → <code>views.subjectline.content</code></li>
<li><code>HTMLBody</code> → <code>views.html.content</code></li>
<li><code>CategoryID</code> → <code>category.id</code></li>
<li><code>IsHTMLPaste=true</code> → assetType <code>208 htmlemail</code></li>
<li>Template slots + parent template → assetType <code>207 htmlemail</code> with <code>views.html.template</code></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>rest207from4:</strong> Enter your parent Content Builder template ID (type 4).</p>
